    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that seems a bit vague though. i feel like there's a lot of evidence that these extra benefits actually discourage people from taking low-wage jobs or even looking for work at all. don't you think the \"disincentive\" factor is a bigger driver of the numbers than the benefits actually help people?",
